rs to trade him<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mysanantonio.com/sports/spurs/article/Sources-Kawhi-Leonard-asks-Spurs-to-trade-him-12997795.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mysanantonio.com%2Fsports%2Fspurs%2Farticle%2FSources-Kawhi-Leonard-asks-Spurs-to-trade-him-12997795.php&d=i%2FJsSzWykDEOeH%2BadX%2B7WnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=2c0b2535\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mysanantonio.com/sports/spurs/article/Sources-Kawhi-Leonard-asks-Spurs-to-trade-him-12997795.php</a><br />\n<br />\n聯盟清泉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一早話撚左佢仆街 難為成班盲撐刺狗幫佢兜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}